description.plain:
Theodore Jones, better known by his stage name Young Greatness, was an American rapper from New Orleans.

He is best known for his 2015 single “Moolah,” which peaked at number 85 on the Billboard Hot 100 chart.

He was shot and killed outside of a Waffle House restaurant in New Orleans on October 29, 2018.
